        "action": "Make the oath of allegiance to the King/Monarchy optional for MPs",
        "additional_details": "We think that, at the moment, the political system is biased against republicans. In a democratic society, swearing allegiance to a monarchy should be a choice, not compulsory.",
        "background": "We think that republican politicians should have the option of pledging allegiance to their constituents rather than the Crown.",
